        {
            "_id": "wGJi5YUatY8RTrDN",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Reaction.webp",
            "name": "Rebuking Smoke",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "reaction"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature within 30 feet damages the oath howler</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The oath howler's wound belches foul smoke onto the triggering creature, who must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:30] save. The creature is then immune to that oath howler's Rebuking Smoke for 1 minute.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Dazzled] for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is dazzled for 1 round and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is sickened 1 and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Blinded] until the sickened condition ends.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "air"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "BM3e2F4u21A4JXkI",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Storm of Blasphemies",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The oath howler roars in a @Template[type:cone|distance:30], shouting dozens of pejoratives in as many languages. Creatures in the area take @Damage[10d8[sonic]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[fortitude|dc:33|basic] save). Creatures that critically fail also take @Damage[2d8[persistent,sonic]|options:area-damage] damage and are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Deafened] until the persistent damage ends.</p>\n<p>The oath howler can't use this ability again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge this ability]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
